{"tid":612113,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梁詠琪炮製比卡超蛋糕慶生 小朋友超開心","createTime":"2018-03-31T15:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T15:49:45.000Z","uid":35964,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bc54ce6c483cefee5a9b7ce0f8183c0bb797bd84","tid":612113,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T15:44:12.000Z","msg":"梁詠琪（GiGi）今日42歲生日，她在社交平台貼上炮製生日蛋糕及慶生照，留言：「今天與經理人的小孩一起慶祝生日，這次給小孩子做了一個比卡超蛋糕，很有滿足感！從來沒有玩過pokemon的我，第一次感覺自己和比卡超那麼近！」<br />\n<br />\n除了經理人的小孩開心外，GiGi的3歲女兒Sofia都很好奇，走上前指著比卡超的臉蛋。網民就幾乎不相信是她造的，大讚「超勁」！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180325/_2018032518144432625.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180325%2F_2018032518144432625.jpg&h=6f7cbc26&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8157c2de4c48e2b845659cf75a086813a06d0e62","tid":612113,"uid":104218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T15:46:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">西班牙籍老公Sergio個西班牙籍香港老婆Sergigi</span></span>"},{"pid":"3b54ad287e1e89addd39108ab5152f6e9995b78f","tid":612113,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T15:47:36.000Z","msg":"隻比卡超好似打開對腳等俾人屌咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"526c83b626da51f05ef9346f6646e556f2482020","tid":612113,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b54ad287e1e89addd39108ab5152f6e9995b78f","tid":612113,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T15:47:36.000Z","msg":"隻比卡超好似打開對腳等俾人屌咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T15:48:56.000Z","msg":"駱駝咁"},{"pid":"2170e7bff0c67c2cdf26d3f0e77d99f41263ecdd","tid":612113,"uid":24457,"like